## File Organization

### Directory Structure
```
project/
├── docs/
│   └── images/
│       ├── architecture/
│       ├── diagrams/
│       └── screenshots/
├── designs/
│   ├── mockups/
│   └── wireframes/
├── demos/
│   └── videos/
└── assets/
    └── generated/
```

### Naming Convention
- **Diagrams**: `[type]-[description]-[version].png`
  - Example: `flowchart-auth-flow-v1.png`
- **Mockups**: `[screen]-mockup-[version].png`
  - Example: `dashboard-mockup-v2.png`
- **Videos**: `[content]-demo-[date].mp4`
  - Example: `checkout-demo-20251017.mp4`

